FBIS3-19883 "drweu056_n_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 NORDIC COUNTRIES Denmark * Private Foreign Aid Agencies Increase Spending 94EN0252C Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE in Danish 1 Mar 94 p 7 94EN0252C Copenhagen BERLINGSKE TIDENDE Language: Danish Article Type:CSO [Unattributed report: "More Aid"] [Text] The four private aid organizations -- the State Church System's Emergency Aid, Ibis, the Danish Red Cross, and the Labor Unions' Developing Countries Secretariat -- will spend 67.3 billion kroner more of DANIDA's [Danish International Development Authority] funds this year than the Folketing anticipated last year.
